This paper discusses extensions to the RDF data model and SPARQL query language that aim to address usability and data management shortcomings of RDF reification. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and deep learning (cs.DL).
